<D>__{i heard about that deal for your father you must be real proud.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{sure.}
<C>__{zack}
<D>__{the stories people tell, he was a real colorful fella }
<C>__{patrolman }
<D>__{zack! we got one!}
<C>__{zack}
<D>__{well back on the clock. you see any of our neighbors from the south, let 'em know i'm lookin' for 'em.}
